Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION

Title: Relates to modernizing the chiropractic scope of practice; repealer
Summary: Expands the scope of chiropractic practice; authorizes chiropractic clinical assistants.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to modernizing the chiropractic scope of practice; and to repeal certain provisions of such law relating thereto
